LOTUS PHARMACEUT June Sales Fall 23.70% (Table) : 1795 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-08T07:25:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/lotus-pharmaceut-june-sales-fall-23-70-table-1795-tt.html
LOTUS PHARMACEUT said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 23.70% to NT$36,644,000 from NT$48,027,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             36,644           48,027    
YOY%             -23.70%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            233,117          285,969    
YOY%             -18.48% 
=================================================================
 